    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Numeric, alphanumeric, or other identifying codes assigned when an art object, book, or other item is described or listed in a catalog, usually a published catalog. An example is an exhibition catalog. The numbers are typically not marked on the object itself. For numbers given to objects when they are acquired by a repository, prefer "accession numbers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
